727230f-a.title: Queens: Liberty Avenue - 132nd Street
727230f-a.text:
Aiberty Avenue, south side, west from 132nd Street (formerly
Atfleld Street). Also shown are (left) homes on the west side
of the last mentioned Street. All bdildings in this view, with
the exception of the peaked roof house on Liberty Avenue, were
non-existent in i9i3.
May 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
